---
By: Naong Hyegeun
Source:
  Title: Cooking Your Way to Enlightnment with Korean Buddhist Nun and Chef
    Beop Song
  By: Julia Hirsch
  Contributor: Beop Song
  Publisher: Tricycle
  URL: https://tricycle.org/trikedaily/cooking-way-enlightenment-beop-song/
  Date: October 5, 2017
Format: verse
---
The green mountain asks me to live in silence
The blue sky asks me to live without dust
Letting go of anger and letting go of greed
They ask me to live and go away
Just like the stream and like the wind
